yingyinNormal.en: One candidate lays low so the other gets his or her moment in the spotlight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一名候选人保持低调，让另一名候选人得到最大关注。

yingyinNormal.en: You want a candidate with a family. We are after the woman's vote.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想要有完整家庭的候选人。我们要抢的就是女性选民的选票。

yingyinNormal.en: The election is in eight months, the debates in six, and the candidate announcement, Monday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 8个月后选举，6个月后辩论宣布候选人，周一。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, if you wanna work with us on this bill, I can stomach a gun friendly candidate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你愿意在法案上与我们合作，我就能容忍一个爱枪的候选人。

yingyinNormal.en: Every advisor and consultant and staff member would beg a presidential candidate not to say them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每一个幕僚，顾问和下属都不希望总统候选人说这种话。

yingyinNormal.en: You are the ideal Dartmouth candidate. Thank you, sir. And it would be an honor to attend Dartmouth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是达特茅斯理想的候选人。谢谢，我很荣幸能够去达特茅斯。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's make this build. Once it gets out, I'll make sure the Republicans don't come to my candidate's defense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让事情发酵。消息一曝光，我会确保共和党人不会拥护我的候选人。

yingyinNormal.en: It's all yours. And don't forget your membership proposal. Try picking a more suitable candidate this time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这交给你了，还有不要忘了上交候选人提名。这次尽量挑个更合适的人选。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, before you react, just listen. You are the most likely candidate at this point. You were distraught, you were drinking.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先别激动，听我说。目前你是最有可能的候选人。你当时心烦意乱，还酗酒。

yingyinNormal.en: We would want to settle on a candidate soon, someone who the whole party can get behind like the Republicans are getting behind Mendoza.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们想尽快确定候选人，能为全党保驾护航的人，就像共和党的门多萨。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, Mark, we asked you back here because we've come into possession of a second audio recording of your candidate on an airplane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 马克，我们再次请你来是因为我们又拿到了一份录音是你的候选人在飞机上说的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it's not like that in the United States. I'm not running because I can do things a candidate can't do, like this proposal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国可不是这样，我不竞选，是因为我能做到总统候选人做不到的事，比如这份提议。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the plan? I stand before you this evening as vice presidential candidate, as the First Lady of the United States, and most of all as a citizen of this great country.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么计划？今晚我站在你们面前，做作为副总统候选人，作为美国的第一夫人，最重要的，也作为这个伟大国度的一名公民。

yingyinNormal.en: Miss Clark, why should I employ you, instead of, say, the previous candidate?
yingyinNormal.zh: 克拉克小姐，我为什么要雇佣你，而不是之前来面试的人？

yingyinNormal.en: Welcome to the Astronaut Candidate Program. Now pay attention, because this could save your life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欢迎来到宇航员预备计划，现在请注意听, 因为可能会救你一命。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know whom she would have selected as the father, but no doubt she had a candidate in mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道她到时会找谁做孩子的父亲，但毫无疑问 ，她心里肯定有人选。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, the leadership wants him, and we've played nice, but the president and I want Cathy Durant. She's a much stronger candidate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 领导层想要他，我们也配合了他们，但我和总统想要的是凯茜·杜兰特，她参选要更有希望。

yingyinNormal.en: Your hypothalamus is swimming in a soup of estrogen and progesterone and suddenly even Leonard seems like a viable sexual candidate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的下丘脑里正游走着雌激素和孕激素，这时突然在你眼里就算莱纳德也会是一名有生育能力的性对象。

yingyinNormal.en: Now think of it, it's 2016 and the leading candidate releases not only her four years of back tax returns, but also her personal genome. And it looks really good. And then she challenges all of her competitors to do the same.
yingyinNormal.zh: 假设，现在是2016年，竞选人不仅公开她四年的税后申报，还有她的个人基因组，看上去很不错。然后她要求其他的竞争者也这么做。
